# Web Interface

The web interface provides a dashboard and API for interacting with the CarbonSense system.

## Main Components

- [app.py](mdc:src/carbonsense/web/app.py): Contains the FastAPI application implementing the web dashboard and REST API endpoints.
- [run_server.py](mdc:src/carbonsense/web/run_server.py): Provides utilities for starting and configuring the web server.

## Frontend Assets

- [templates/](mdc:src/carbonsense/web/templates): Contains HTML templates for the web dashboard.
- [static/](mdc:src/carbonsense/web/static): Contains static assets like CSS, JavaScript, and images.

For more details about using the web interface, check the [web README.md](mdc:src/carbonsense/web/README.md) file.

